1509570\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610430/extras/df4902cb98a14012d8f31aa8d1d9180f.webm?t=1771509570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610430/extras/df4902cb98a14012d8f31aa8d1d9180f.mp4?t=1771509570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fortifications for the defense of the Base.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610430/extras/b469c68139a852e6ff4b06e8e221f878.poster.avif?t=1771509570\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610430/extras/b469c68139a852e6ff4b06e8e221f878.webm?t=1771509570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610430/extras/b469c68139a852e6ff4b06e8e221f878.mp4?t=1771509570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vehicles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610430/extras/2eb1ed364f50052e48ecf880fa00b66e.poster.avif?t=1771509570\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610430/extras/2eb1ed364f50052e48ecf880fa00b66e.webm?t=1771509570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1610430/extras/2eb1ed364f50052e48ecf880fa00b66e.mp4?t=1771509570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OPG: Clan Wars offers a variety of game modes so that everyone can find something to their liking. You can play Arena Shooter on limited locations, where you can fight with other players and show your skills in battle. Also awaits you online survival simulator in the open world, where you will have to search for resources, build a shelter and defend yourself from the dangers that await you at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive in harsh conditions in online multiplayer or single-player mode. Collect weapons, tools and resources, hidden unique items, mysterious and dangerous dungeons and locations filled with various valuable loot that will help you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore secret, underground laboratories, life forms of unknown origin, mysterious search for artifacts that challenge our knowledge of the laws of nature - all this is a huge world of one of several game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The presence of cars and trucks will help players to move quickly through open locations and have an advantage over the enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique combination of Weapons - from modern automatic pistols, militaristic assault rifles, brutal large-caliber weapons, classic historical weapons - a huge combination of killing tools to satisfy any player.</p>",
